          <h1>SCHEDULING</h1>
          <h2>Trusted by Simon Fraser University</h2>
          <hr class="aboutHR">
          <p class="ct-u-size22 ct-u-fontWeight300 ct-u-marginBottom60 marginTop40">
          <h4> Why we chose this for our project</h4>
          <p class = "script">This website was created to make booking appointments for SFU students simpler. Also, this website allows educators to have an easy method of posting their availability.</p>

          <h4> Who can use this webiste?</h4>
          <p>Students can use the website to book appointments for TAs, professors, advisors etc. As a SFU student, they would have access to a calendar and book whatever appointment they need. As an SFU educator, they can use the website to post whatever time they would be available and cancel appointments whenever necessary.</p>

          <h4>How is this website used?</h4>
          <p><i>Students</i> - will need to sign up or sign in to an acccount. After they sign in, they would have access to a calendar, and by clicking on the selected date, they would have to fill out an online form to select which staff member and what time they want.</p>
          <p><i> Educators </i> - will need to sign up or sign in to an account. After the sign in, they would have access to a calendar, and by clicking the "New Meeting" link, they would need to give what dates and times they would be available to meet with students.</p>
        </div>
